Depends: pcd-templates, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Linter for Post-Coding Development specifications
 pcd-lint validates specification files written in the Post-Coding Development
 (PCD) paradigm format. It enforces structural rules, semantic validation, and
 cross-section consistency checks.
